Tissuespecific by effect:

Also, plot the number of tissues in which a gene has the same sign:

samesign=apply(pm.mash.beta.norm,1,function(x){sum(x>0)})
hist(samesign,main="",xlab="NumberofTissues",breaks=0.5:44.5,col="grey",freq=FALSE,xaxt="n")
axis(1, at=seq(1, 44, by=1), labels=c(1:44))
